implement executable awareness for lua

From: Skye Soss <skye@soss.website>

Add the new configuration variable LUA_USE_EXECAWARE, which controls the use of
execveat() and the securebits. Adds the new function luaL_loadfile_exec, which
queries EXEC_RESTRICT_FILE securebit, which is used in lua.c. The
EXEC_DENY_INTERPRET securebit is checked before starting the REPL, performing
the -e command line option, or handling the LUA_INIT environment variable.
